Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.12,0:01:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is a question about experience. When I saw up on the chart the different qualities of divinity, the experience of those qualities seems to be different than the experience of the functioning of allness, the oneness.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.19,0:01:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If the qualities are different from the functioning of the wholeness, and that's the difference in the experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.32,0:01:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The wholeness and the oneness doesn't function. It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.46,0:01:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.02,0:01:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Isness doesn't function, doesn't do. There's no this to do with that. That's a dualistic conception.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.30,0:01:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The qualities of divinity are not the same as the essence of divinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.50,0:01:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Five foot eight by 110 pounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.72,0:01:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not your essence, it's a quality.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.59,0:02:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So divinity, the feeling of it is, even the presence of love is overwhelming.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.06,0:02:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,At the same time, infinitely powerful cannot be described.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.58,0:02:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be like describing an infinitely powerful powder puff. There's no way to really explain it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.46,0:02:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's infinitely powerful and exquisite and irresistible and omnipotent.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.55,0:02:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It is omnipotent.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.86,0:02:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's infinitely powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.88,0:02:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,At the same time, exquisitely loving and gentle, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.86,0:02:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure you're talking to both microphones.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.87,0:02:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Put them closer together, maybe, so they don't clank.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.25,0:02:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you get feedback.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.23,0:02:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.46,0:02:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,First, thank you for that answer to my friend's question about the anxiety, because I'm going to have to play that over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.22,0:03:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.93,0:03:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This question has to do with a job, again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.49,0:03:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a chance to pursue...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.31,0:03:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A job that was very linear, lots of left brain material, and I decided not to because I didn't want to put all my energy into that,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.99,0:03:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,all my focus right now, at this point, into all that left brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.85,0:03:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Detail, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.21,0:03:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So, can something like that actually hinder you spiritually if you don't feel inclined to go there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.22,0:03:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't make a rule about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.20,0:03:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,At one time, forcing yourself into...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.62,0:03:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sequential linearity could, you know, will slow down the process
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.46,0:03:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and shift your attention and energy elsewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.21,0:03:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,that might be doing better in a more non-linear awareness consciousness program, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.44,0:03:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.38,0:03:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it just depends where you are in your life and what you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.66,0:04:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it depends on a multitude of factors.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.82,0:04:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think it can really be answered.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.30,0:04:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, I have a stack of things in my desk at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.78,0:04:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, I can't get into it this week.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.30,0:04:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I got a lecture Saturday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.56,0:04:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my excuse this week.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.38,0:04:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Next week, I'll find a new excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.92,0:04:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.86,0:04:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a reluctance as you get more advanced.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.28,0:04:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There's like a reluctance to get into linear memorization and that kind of thing
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.28,0:04:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,because you're trying to be left brain when your energies are moving more right brain holistically.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.35,0:04:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It would have felt more like going to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.49,0:04:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.84,0:04:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.62,0:04:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see that, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.88,0:04:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a conflict, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.66,0:04:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.26,0:04:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.88,0:05:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,When I'm reading something of yours or listening to one of your lectures and I'm stuck and I know I can't understand what it is you're trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.52,0:05:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The issue is moralistic relativity and also...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.08,0:05:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What issue is what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.36,0:05:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Moralistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.40,0:05:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm getting...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.34,0:05:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, moral relativism.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.14,0:05:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Relativism, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.82,0:05:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.24,0:05:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.44,0:05:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't even get it, say it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.04,0:05:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's pretty much a good sign that I'm suffering from it when I can't understand what you're trying to teach about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.18,0:05:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I'm wondering if I may have started to seek some clarity or if you can clean me up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.26,0:05:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm wondering...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.38,0:05:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me what you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.52,0:05:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even know what you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.34,0:05:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.86,0:05:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Straighten up what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.64,0:05:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You promised moral relativism?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.36,0:05:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What is your problem with moral relativism?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.02,0:05:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's rather clear and obvious, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.25,0:05:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's true if I say it's true and it's not true if I say it's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.45,0:06:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And morality is idiotic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.41,0:06:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an impairment of my entitlement to express myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.22,0:06:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Any way I want, because we have freedom of speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.29,0:06:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And physical physicality is symbolic speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.77,0:06:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you like my freedom to choke you to death?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.58,0:06:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.48,0:06:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You see what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.18,0:06:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.72,0:06:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, there's no limitation, no wall that differentiates a livable environment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.70,0:06:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There's truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.02,0:06:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,At each level, there's its own truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.50,0:06:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, is there...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.54,0:06:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there that same moralistic...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.57,0:06:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the MR.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.54,0:06:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The MR.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.44,0:06:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that occur at each level?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.18,0:06:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Or is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.66,0:06:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.05,0:06:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Relativism.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.54,0:06:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.68,0:07:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Moral relativism is below 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.63,0:07:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.45,0:07:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Over 200 doesn't make any sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.03,0:07:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.87,0:07:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.17,0:07:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why the Ninth Circuit Court of Appeals calibrates very low.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.84,0:07:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If I say, you know, we have free speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.08,0:07:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If I say, action is symbolic speech, then I'm entitled to any action I want, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.26,0:07:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Because there's no right or wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.16,0:07:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no criteria.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.26,0:07:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There's actually no law.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.68,0:07:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What you've just done is undone the nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.54,0:07:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.92,0:07:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Because now the nation has nothing upon which to rely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.46,0:07:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the law, then, is just merely relativism.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.72,0:07:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have to obey the law, because that's a restriction of my freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.21,0:07:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And I have freedom of expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.35,0:07:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.77,0:07:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.35,0:07:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's absolute...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.13,0:07:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's also absolute truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.55,0:07:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, that's what kind of supersedes that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.29,0:08:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what they're talking about are statements, and statements about action.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,0:08:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not talking about truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.61,0:08:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,They're talking about moral laws.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.11,0:08:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,They're just playing a game, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.41,0:08:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,In a way?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.39,0:08:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,An ego game?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.77,0:08:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Lewis Carroll.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.35,0:08:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a looking glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.49,0:08:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.72,0:08:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The Mad Hatter says, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.16,0:08:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it was the Mad Hatter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.26,0:08:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.66,0:08:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The rabbit says, when I say a word, it means what I mean it to mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.24,0:08:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing more, nothing less.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.83,0:08:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The Mad Hatter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.71,0:08:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The Mad Hatter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.45,0:08:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're setting yourself up almost as divinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.94,0:08:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Reality is what I say is reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.16,0:08:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's not reality if I say it's not reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.19,0:08:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's the absurdity of the Mad Hatter that I pointed out to illustrate the absurdity of moral relativism.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.77,0:08:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Because moral relativism says that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.99,0:08:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,logic and reason are what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.10,0:09:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,An infringement of one's freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.39,0:09:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But if all statements are questionable and untrue, then so is that statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.71,0:09:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Moral relativism has nothing to stand on because, like skepticism, it hangs itself by its own petard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.15,0:09:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's no standard of truth, then the criticism of truth also has no standard upon which to stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.36,0:09:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.34,0:09:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what the rabbit has to say today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.42,0:09:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The Mad Hatter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.40,0:09:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The Mad Hatter, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.72,0:09:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The Mad Hatter said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.14,0:09:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.70,0:09:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.53,0:09:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.96,0:09:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You mentioned earlier that the chances were 1,000% easier now to reach enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.84,0:10:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it getting easier to stay physical after enlightenment than it used to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.45,0:10:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.78,0:10:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The chances of reaching enlightenment are 1,000 times greater.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.70,0:10:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That we confirm many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.14,0:10:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.82,0:10:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.88,0:10:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.94,0:10:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.00,0:10:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.02,0:10:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.04,0:10:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.10,0:10:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.12,0:10:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.14,0:10:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.16,0:10:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.18,0:10:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.20,0:10:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.22,0:10:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.24,0:10:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.26,0:10:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.28,0:10:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.52,0:10:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.54,0:10:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.58,0:10:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.42,0:10:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.50,0:10:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.58,0:10:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.66,0:10:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.78,0:10:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.82,0:10:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.88,0:10:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.90,0:10:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.04,0:10:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.14,0:10:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what question to ask about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.92,0:10:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I always feel, within myself, that there's like a, prior to this incarnation, there was
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.82,0:10:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,a commitment, an agreement, an understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.97,0:10:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I find myself holding back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.47,0:10:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Holding back what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.59,0:10:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,From wanting to reach enlightenment, because I don't want to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.52,0:10:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You got a little work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.22,0:10:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm too attached.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.24,0:10:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hehehe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.78,0:10:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hehehe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.79,0:10:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Now eventually the body becomes immaterial.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.82,0:11:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If it keeps walking on, that's fine, and if it don't keep walking on, because you don't
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.52,0:11:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,even know what it's going to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.98,0:11:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The personal will doesn't even intervene.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.58,0:11:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I can remember walking down the aisle and turning around and didn't know whether one
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.42,0:11:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,would get to the end or not, out of curiosity, watch what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.51,0:11:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I made 180 at the end and walked back again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.79,0:11:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Other times the body will breathe again or it won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.29,0:11:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's immaterial which way it goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.19,0:11:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No, if it breathes, it breathes, and if it doesn't, it doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.91,0:11:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Many times I've been just waiting to die and sat there waiting to leave, and it didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.50,0:11:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.36,0:11:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.36,0:11:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The smoke is shooting out from the engine on fire, the smoke behind the dashboard, you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.34,0:11:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.42,0:12:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There I am out, a million miles from anywhere, it's 110 out, I'm dehydrated, I've got nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.40,0:12:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,An annoyingness came from within.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.74,0:12:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a screwdriver and jam it through the bottom of the glove compartment, wham.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.34,0:12:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Now there's a couple of drops of coffee left in there, pour it through there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.76,0:12:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I poured it through there, I was just sitting there waiting to leave, it said to do that,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.25,0:12:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,so I did that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.76,0:12:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Psst, the fire went out, it was an electrical fire, and the point where I drove the car
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.20,0:12:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,with the screwdriver was exactly over the fire, underneath the hood, the electrical
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.96,0:12:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,done on my old truck over the last 30 years, it was like a mass of wires, just the left
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.00,0:12:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,brain never could attract where it was coming from.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.92,0:12:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So was that asked for?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.28,0:12:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.28,0:12:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It just came on to do that, and I did that, and so the body's still going.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.46,0:12:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So you surrender your life to God, surrender your body to God, surrender your life to God,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.93,0:12:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,whether it walks on or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.61,0:12:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been up to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.61,0:13:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you have a karmic role to play, you will obviously play it, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.23,0:13:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you don't, you leave, so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.08,0:13:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,As I said, here's this mind right here, you know, and this guy looks at me, and we're
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.44,0:13:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,looking at each other, he says, well, what if we don't, we can't keep it away from the
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.34,0:13:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.34,0:13:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, so we die.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.34,0:13:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, he says, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.34,0:13:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The total acceptance of it, he accepted it, and then I accepted it because of my experience
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.73,0:13:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,in the snowbank.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.73,0:13:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But in the energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.80,0:13:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,In the energy of the acceptance, he was able to accept it, and he said, oh, yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.94,0:13:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.94,0:13:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay if you want to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.94,0:13:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You can leave anything you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.00,0:13:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you can hang in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.00,0:13:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't matter much to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.03,0:13:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.54,0:13:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You got permission to stay as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.98,0:13:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to feel guilty about staying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.98,0:13:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people feel guilty that they haven't died yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.98,0:13:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.98,0:13:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.58,0:13:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a fun question.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.58,0:13:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.58,0:13:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you to both of you for all of the work you've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.58,0:13:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,On a couple of your Cs, I'm going to ask you a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.58,0:13:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to ask you a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.58,0:13:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to ask you a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.99,0:14:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to ask you a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.99,0:14:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to ask you a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.99,0:14:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,On a couple of your CDs, you mention a couple of phrases that I particularly like, like
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.94,0:14:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,so I put them on a T-shirt for you, so, so what, and then it seemed like a good idea
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.80,0:14:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.80,0:14:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Seemed like a good idea at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.80,0:14:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.80,0:14:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.80,0:14:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how you forgive yourself for everything in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.80,0:14:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It seemed like a good idea at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.62,0:14:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.62,0:14:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I also heard that you like fortune cookies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.62,0:14:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I mean, the toy business is all electronic fortune cookies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.62,0:14:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I would just give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.62,0:14:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.62,0:14:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.62,0:14:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.62,0:14:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,My question, I apologize for it, because I know a lot of people have asked it over the
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.12,0:14:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,months, but I still don't quite get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.62,0:14:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And you mentioned that your time of death is preset.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.62,0:14:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.62,0:15:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And then on some of the tapes, you also talk about, you know, extreme sports or even the
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.94,0:15:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,colleagues you knew who lived in a bubble and kept getting smaller and smaller.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.94,0:15:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The things they'd eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.94,0:15:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I'm a bit confused on if your time of death is set, why the extreme sports would
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.18,0:15:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,make a difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.18,0:15:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.18,0:15:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What would make a difference?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.18,0:15:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,When you said extreme sports.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.18,0:15:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Extreme sports.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.43,0:15:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If your time of death is already destined, set, then why would extreme sports make a
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.43,0:15:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,difference?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.43,0:15:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the means of it is not set.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.28,0:15:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hypothetically, there would seem to be a disparity there, see, but if you get into a context
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.04,0:15:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,beyond the two alternates.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.04,0:15:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a this versus a that, then you'll see they're both the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.44,0:15:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.62,0:15:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes there's a, see, the deeper the fear, the greater the length you gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.54,0:16:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people have to go over Niagara Falls in a barrel to overcome that fear, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.06,0:16:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see extremes to overcome that fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.64,0:16:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,People are driven to mad, mad extremes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.14,0:16:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, some mountain where 76 people have already died.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.34,0:16:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You go up to that peak, and here they are at 20,000 feet with no oxygen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.85,0:16:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm looking, and they got a coach with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.00,0:16:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is this coach's head taking people up there at 18,000 feet with no oxygen?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.06,0:16:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course they're gonna get exhausted, of course they're gonna get confused, and they
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.80,0:16:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,charge money for that as a guide?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.30,0:16:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I want a refund.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.10,0:16:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I want oxygen over 10, you know, in a plane over 10,000 you get oxygen, not 18,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.99,0:16:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Kilimanjaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.99,0:16:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,How many has Kilimanjaro killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.35,0:17:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,How many people have died trying to climb Kilimanjaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.79,0:17:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hundreds.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.33,0:17:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Look it up, it's sort of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.24,0:17:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Slew of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.04,0:17:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the weight of certain death, okay, let's get back and go on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.69,0:17:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you also be willing to calibrate how much the consciousness of the group raised
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.95,0:17:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,today?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.56,0:17:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The consciousness of the group?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.44,0:17:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't done that in a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.68,0:17:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, no, but I know what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.11,0:17:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The great books of the Western world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.33,0:17:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We're at the level of the great books of the Western world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.63,0:17:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,How's that for erudition?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.36,0:17:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We're over the great books of the Western world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.08,0:17:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The consciousness level of this crowd is beyond that of the great books of the Western world,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.58,0:17:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,the collective wisdom of mankind throughout the ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.20,0:17:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So we've evolved then into, the group has evolved into the 500s.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.08,0:17:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The group's gone into the 500s.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.34,0:18:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.34,0:18:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,See, there's a couple of major jumps.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.84,0:18:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,200.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.96,0:18:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, then to get out of emotionality, running your life and get to rationality at 400.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.80,0:18:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Then to get out of linear cause and effect, which is the Newtonian paradigm at 499.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.34,0:18:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And the hardest jump is to make the jump from the 400s to the 500s.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.42,0:18:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the hardest one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.42,0:18:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And a group like this naturally, yeah, evolves into the 500s.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.54,0:18:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we allowed to get photos?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.00,0:18:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have a photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.00,0:18:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.98,0:18:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I stand next to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.98,0:18:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.98,0:18:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Robert will help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.74,0:18:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He's good at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.84,0:18:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.84,0:18:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You want, you want to be in the picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.84,0:18:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.20,0:18:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,See, you want to be in the picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.20,0:18:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.20,0:18:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's my quack quack?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.77,0:18:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's my, anyway, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.77,0:18:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Doc, look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.77,0:18:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Your fortune cookie.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.77,0:18:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.77,0:18:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,My quack quack.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.77,0:18:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Computerized fortune cookie, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.12,0:18:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember what we said the calibrated level of fortune cookies was?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.12,0:18:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.12,0:18:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, honey, your book.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.12,0:19:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,350 or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.12,0:19:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.12,0:19:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.12,0:19:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.72,0:19:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.72,0:19:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.72,0:19:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.72,0:19:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.72,0:19:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.72,0:19:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.72,0:19:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.72,0:19:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.63,0:19:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Next question.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.68,0:19:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if someone is on the spiritual path, and at the end of their life goes into a negative
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.60,0:19:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,dimension.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that mean for the consciousness?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.23,0:19:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody's what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.23,0:19:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,In a spiritual path and at the end of their life or towards the end of their life, they
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.92,0:19:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,go into a negative...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.92,0:19:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.46,0:19:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They fall, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.46,0:19:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, they would then have the karma propensities of a person at that level.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.70,0:19:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We see that in the so called fallen gurus.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.11,0:19:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.11,0:19:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm thinking of one now that hit 600 and then crashed below 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.17,0:19:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking of another one that was in the 500, again crashed below 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.26,0:20:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So the great temptations come up, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.06,0:20:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The great temptations.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.16,0:20:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And as I said, as the Buddha called it, demons are looking through the chinks in your armor
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.75,0:20:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,to see where you're susceptible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.89,0:20:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Vanity will give you a title, Grand Maha, Grand Mahatma.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.89,0:20:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And then we'll give you swirly clothes, and we'll let people go, wah, wah, wah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.21,0:20:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And if that don't get you, then we'll try your money.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.37,0:20:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll pour money on you and see if that gets you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.37,0:20:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And if that don't get you, how about a slinky girl who says,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.84,0:20:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,sex is holy, let's get holy, you know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.64,0:20:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So it keeps looking for a chunk, or vanity, vanity, vanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.16,0:20:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It keeps looking for where to get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.78,0:20:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember I explained to you the knowingness that came.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.48,0:20:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you're not karmically answerable, all power is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.69,0:21:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,See, because love is a constraint.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.78,0:21:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of love, you'll only go so far with people.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.34,0:21:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But just your love of other people as fellow humans will curtail you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.08,0:21:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't tear them to pieces with your teeth that you would below 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.15,0:21:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So this was a temptation of power.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.61,0:21:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And I remember, as I said, it was like a high pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.31,0:21:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I could see who had been through there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.49,0:21:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And I saw Jesus Christ went there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.49,0:21:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw exactly what he went through.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.41,0:21:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,All power is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.89,0:21:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,All you have to do is be willing to sell out integrity and honor
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.05,0:21:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and buy stocks in the right company.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.57,0:21:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking about a dementia, you know, a brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.57,0:21:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Dementia, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.55,0:21:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that kind of deterioration.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.35,0:21:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.97,0:21:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's of a different level.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.37,0:21:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,See, there are levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.45,0:21:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,There's the physical, mental, and spiritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.81,0:21:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, physicality.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.49,0:22:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Physicality would have a different karmic propensity, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.81,0:22:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and it takes a genetic pattern, very often genetic pattern.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.61,0:22:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The person within is unaffected, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.89,0:22:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and I used to be the only psychiatrist that would go to all the nursing homes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.09,0:22:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,in Yavapai County.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.99,0:22:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm away home from the girls' ranch.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.71,0:22:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I had all of them all the way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.07,0:22:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I ever got home before dark, I don't know,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.65,0:22:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,but 30,000 miles a year running around.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.50,0:22:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And the family would be all upset because mother, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.40,0:22:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,was forgetful and all this, didn't recognize me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.98,0:22:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's their ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.00,0:22:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It just got hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.83,0:22:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say, mother, how is it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.59,0:22:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, they're very nice to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.49,0:22:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.15,0:22:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, do they treat you well?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.69,0:22:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.79,0:22:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to be someplace else?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.21,0:22:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.97,0:22:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I think this is just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.06,0:22:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She's perfectly at serenity and peace,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.12,0:22:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and I always feel like the spirit is already half gone over.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.12,0:22:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If she were agitated, would that be a different?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.68,0:22:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Agitation would be a different thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.38,0:22:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be a reaction to it, and therefore,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.92,0:22:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,you could treat the agitation, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.96,0:23:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wondering about the karmic implications of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.27,0:23:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.63,0:23:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.05,0:23:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd have to do a little research on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.91,0:23:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.13,0:23:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt that your spiritual destiny is going to be determined
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.26,0:23:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,by the linear physicality of its expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.28,0:23:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.34,0:23:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as we remember who we are, we're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.94,0:23:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Just remember that you're you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.52,0:23:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody says, who am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.84,0:23:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You say, I'm me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.06,0:23:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.67,0:23:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the test of the cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.74,0:23:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.76,0:23:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I've had this discussion with you lots of times.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.76,0:23:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You just haven't been there, so I thought I'd bring it up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.02,0:23:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.80,0:23:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What discussion?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.76,0:23:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Kind of back to what the lady brought up before
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.50,0:23:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,about the day of our death, our physical death,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.64,0:24:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,is written the day we're born.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.27,0:24:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not written.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.01,0:24:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's recorded?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.35,0:24:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,How do I think of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.49,0:24:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.53,0:24:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If you get a tape of a movie,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.01,0:24:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,the end of the movie is already on the tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.47,0:24:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not an infinite tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.73,0:24:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't go on forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.74,0:24:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So every movie has a terminal point.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.84,0:24:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's sequential.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.86,0:24:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,After this event, this event, this event.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.74,0:24:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And then after this event, that's the end of the movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.92,0:24:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,With that in mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.51,0:24:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I keep wondering about our preoccupation
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.35,0:24:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,with this physical death.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.11,0:24:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,When we look at what we like to term disasters,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.51,0:24:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,we have a natural disaster and a thousand people die.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.49,0:24:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We have buildings fall in New York
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.73,0:24:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and thousands of people die.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.65,0:24:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If those occasions hadn't arisen,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.05,0:24:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,wouldn't all of those people have died from a heart attack
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.01,0:24:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,or something that day?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.34,0:24:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a hypothetical.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.48,0:24:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if that's a good question.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.48,0:24:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know that I can answer it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.48,0:24:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I see it more like group karma,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.48,0:24:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,that it's not by accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.48,0:24:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember the bridge of St. Louis Ray?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.48,0:24:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Why were those, what was it, six people or so and so,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.48,0:25:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,crossing the bridge when it collapsed?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.48,0:25:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Why those six people out of all the civilizations?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.48,0:25:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Karmic propensity and influences are hard to explain
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.57,0:25:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,within a logical, linear way.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.73,0:25:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They're subtle and more inferential.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.73,0:25:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You just happen to be
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.73,0:25:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,where those things happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.73,0:25:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you could ask what is the karmic destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.95,0:25:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,of somebody whose house blows down in a hurricane
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.95,0:25:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and immediately they rebuild it in exactly the same place.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.46,0:25:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,California coast, the mudslides.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.46,0:25:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,One expensive house after another falls down.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.23,0:25:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's not that it's a specific day
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.23,0:25:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,these people are going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.23,0:25:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It was after a series of events that they were killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.23,0:25:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's more the fulfillment of a story than a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.23,0:25:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I have permission to ask this.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.23,0:25:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the fulfillment of the story that brings the story to the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.23,0:25:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.23,0:25:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's a good question.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.23,0:25:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.23,0:25:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's not stamped into like a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.23,0:26:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.71,0:26:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And if I might, one more.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.03,0:26:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If in fact there's no cause and effect,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.38,0:26:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,what are we taking responsibility for
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.38,0:26:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,when we're taking responsibility not for only what we do
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.38,0:26:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,but previous lives that we didn't cause?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.38,0:26:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that you're the source, let's say.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.38,0:26:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Not the cause, but you're the source.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.08,0:26:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we share the karmic consequences of that
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.08,0:26:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,which we cheer on and align with.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.10,0:26:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you're a proponent of bullfighting,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.39,0:26:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,then you share somewhat the karmic consequence
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.39,0:26:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,of that which okays cruelty to animals for amusement.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.39,0:26:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,With the bullfighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.42,0:26:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Because what are they getting out of the bullfight?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.42,0:26:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Amusement.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.84,0:26:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,An amusing afternoon for you, but not for the bull, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.84,0:26:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And often not for the matador either.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.84,0:26:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless they adopt children afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.84,0:27:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.18,0:27:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,On several occasions now,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.18,0:27:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,while doing A Course in Miracle lessons,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.18,0:27:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear a voice and my question is whether or not
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.18,0:27:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I should completely ignore this?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.18,0:27:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean here? Auditory?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.27,0:27:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.27,0:27:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of things does it say to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.70,0:27:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,On a couple of occasions,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.70,0:27:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,it's kind of pointing me to read something
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.70,0:27:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,or go someplace.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.70,0:27:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And other times it's maybe more fearful things.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.70,0:27:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like an inner voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.70,0:27:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.90,0:27:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's experienced as though it's auditory.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.90,0:27:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.90,0:27:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.25,0:27:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see what we can figure that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.25,0:27:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.11,0:27:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I intuit what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.11,0:27:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.10,0:27:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.20,0:27:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'm holding is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.20,0:27:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.20,0:27:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a segmentation.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.20,0:27:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a segmentation off of a piece of the personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.20,0:28:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd own it back as yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.26,0:28:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I put faith in what I hear
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.98,0:28:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,or just kind of observe it?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.98,0:28:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.98,0:28:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's got nothing to do with what the content.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.98,0:28:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.98,0:28:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to do with the phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.98,0:28:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.53,0:28:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So I have permission to ask this.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.53,0:28:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a dissociated aspect of its own personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.53,0:28:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a dissociated aspect of your own personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.56,0:28:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a separate self?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.56,0:28:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Like you've separated off from it
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.56,0:28:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,as though it is not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.56,0:28:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it's a dissociated small little part
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.51,0:28:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,of your personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.51,0:28:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.28,0:28:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd have to see in the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.28,0:28:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd have to lay down on the couch
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.28,0:28:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,in a couple of years and figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.28,0:28:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.28,0:28:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.76,0:28:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the way I heal it is I would deny
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.98,0:28:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,that it's separate from yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.98,0:28:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and own it that it is yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.98,0:28:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And just as...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.98,0:28:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Because even if you heard it through another voice,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.98,0:28:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,it's what you're holding in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.98,0:28:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,that's sounding back to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.98,0:28:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It could be a dissociated thought
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.85,0:29:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,that you don't want to own, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.85,0:29:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So is it as much of an unreality
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.85,0:29:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,as everything else that goes on in one's mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.85,0:29:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no more real nor unreal
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.30,0:29:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,than anything else that goes on in your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.30,0:29:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You have dreams, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.30,0:29:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't mean you're loony.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.30,0:29:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just meaning you're having a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.30,0:29:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're having an auditory dream while you're awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.30,0:29:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.94,0:29:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.94,0:29:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.94,0:29:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Own it back as a portion of your own personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.94,0:29:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's, you know, that that is also me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.54,0:29:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as your dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.67,0:29:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't disown your dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.67,0:29:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Whose dreams are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.67,0:29:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Waking dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.22,0:29:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Waking auditory dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.22,0:29:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Waking auditory dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.22,0:29:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.66,0:29:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.66,0:29:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.66,0:29:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.88,0:29:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That is quick diagnosis.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.88,0:29:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,My goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.88,0:29:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.09,0:29:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for giving this opportunity to come
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.55,0:30:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and be able to say how grateful we are
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.55,0:30:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,to all that you've given to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.06,0:30:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.06,0:30:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonderful gift to have this time with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.22,0:30:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I was interested today as you were talking about,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.74,0:30:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,you were talking about spiritual teachers
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.93,0:30:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and I was, came to mind Victor Frankl
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.93,0:30:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and his experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.93,0:30:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,of having to, having, being able to find grace
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.09,0:30:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,in the middle of hell
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.09,0:30:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and how that relates to your experience of finding grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.22,0:30:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Victor Frankl ended up writing a book.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.22,0:30:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He was at a concentration camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.22,0:30:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.41,0:30:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And he wrote about an aspect of psychology
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.05,0:30:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,that was really very important
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.05,0:30:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and I can't specifically give you the exact name of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.05,0:30:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Logos, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.05,0:30:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's maybe not the book but the concept.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.05,0:30:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Logos therapy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.05,0:30:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's not what it was about.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.12,0:31:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe the title of the book was Man's Search for Meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.12,0:31:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.12,0:31:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.12,0:31:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.12,0:31:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.12,0:31:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That looking for meaning is instinctual.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.25,0:31:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's one of the instincts.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.25,0:31:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Freud did not mention it as an instinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.25,0:31:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He said it's sufficiently powerful
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.25,0:31:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and I think that's true
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.25,0:31:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,because when we talk about spiritual fantasy,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.25,0:31:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,see, it's like people are always looking for meaning
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.25,0:31:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and if they can't find meaning, they'll invent one.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.64,0:31:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Man wants to know what it means.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.64,0:31:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So you get together the facts,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.64,0:31:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,but what do they mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.64,0:31:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So, yes, I liked Frankl
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.64,0:31:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and it was like the will to meaning is instinctual
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.77,0:31:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and I agreed with him for the more advanced.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.25,0:31:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But you see, even primitive man wanted to know
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.25,0:31:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,what is the meaning of a volcano?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.25,0:31:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He invented angry gods and sacrificed maidens.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.60,0:31:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the meaning of natural phenomena?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.60,0:32:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, kinda like the problems and the problems and the answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.30,0:32:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that experience for him
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.30,0:32:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,of finding love and ultimate love in the middle of hell
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.30,0:32:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,similar to the experience you had
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.68,0:32:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,in finding God in the middle of hell
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.68,0:32:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,or was it a different experience?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.68,0:32:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.68,0:32:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, his was an external hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.67,0:32:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Mine was internal.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.67,0:32:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But internally, he experienced probably the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.10,0:32:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Extreme, extreme.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.10,0:32:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.10,0:32:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and I've forgotten about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.55,0:32:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Frankel wrote that man has an instinctive drive
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.49,0:32:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,to discern meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.75,0:32:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.14,0:32:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.98,0:32:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you both.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.34,0:32:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a very hard question for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.14,0:32:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I have intuited that some physical challenges
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.50,0:32:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,that have come up are a karmic undoing.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.02,0:32:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But my question is,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.84,0:33:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,if I surrender the guilt
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.12,0:33:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and ask for a miracle to have the guilt removed,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.70,0:33:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,is that the right spiritual path to take
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.16,0:33:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,or do I need to unwork the karma?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.36,0:33:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,How to process it?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.78,0:33:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I would work on all levels simultaneously.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.31,0:33:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd pray for a miracle to see it as it is in truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.43,0:33:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I would also,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.71,0:33:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I would also pray for whatever the negative side of this is
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.05,0:33:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,within yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.03,0:33:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Assume it's something within yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.64,0:33:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And pray for the opposite of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.00,0:33:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,paradoxically, to undo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.89,0:33:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And keep reaffirming that you're an infinite being
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.39,0:33:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're only subject to what you hold in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.51,0:33:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And forgive yourself for whatever it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.31,0:34:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt like it wasn't just my own guilt,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.95,0:34:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,but that I had an unforgiveness
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.11,0:34:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,from someone stabbing me in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.31,0:34:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.69,0:34:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And back in a past life.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.05,0:34:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And the betrayal of that
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.25,0:34:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,was such a heart pain
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.50,0:34:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,that I haven't been able to let that go.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.40,0:34:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Betrayal.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.12,0:34:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, betrayal.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.86,0:34:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And it wasn't the physical death,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.46,0:34:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,but the betrayal.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.18,0:34:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it was the betrayal.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.66,0:34:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.03,0:34:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so you can undo the betrayal.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.00,0:34:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Think what Jesus Christ must have felt
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.86,0:34:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,when he was kissed by a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.27,0:34:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So you share, you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.57,0:34:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,how Christ suffered for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.60,0:34:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Betrayal by a trusted friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.30,0:34:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, pray for the forgiveness
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.86,0:34:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,of the one in you who betrays others.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.94,0:34:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.63,0:34:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.73,0:34:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.89,0:35:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,How does one best dissolve the duality
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.65,0:35:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,between oneself and God?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.23,0:35:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't a duality.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.37,0:35:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a linguistic event you just recorded.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.86,0:35:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no duality between oneself and God.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.54,0:35:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But it seems that oneself is so small
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.57,0:35:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,in comparison to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.27,0:35:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The personal self.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.92,0:35:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.38,0:35:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, the personal self is small.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.27,0:35:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why they call it the small self.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.19,0:35:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.76,0:35:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a disparity.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.79,0:35:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a disparity.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.69,0:35:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like you are already within that
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.65,0:35:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and have set up some falsity
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.91,0:35:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,so that you don't realize
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.25,0:35:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,that you are at one with the one,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.04,0:35:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,that you're separate from the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.29,0:35:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, it's like,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.97,0:35:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,it just takes constant spiritual work
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.05,0:35:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,of one kind or another
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.97,0:36:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and then eventually that falls away.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.57,0:36:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a matter of seeing oneself as limited?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.16,0:36:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Discrete, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.76,0:36:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.61,0:36:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.24,0:36:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Last month,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.34,0:36:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,you were talking about
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.42,0:36:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,the Buddha came to teach us enlightenment,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.76,0:36:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,but Jesus came to teach us salvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.62,0:36:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you talk a little bit about
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.74,0:36:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,what you mean by salvation?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.48,0:36:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Salvation means that you,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.26,0:36:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,in and of yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.50,0:36:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,haven't earned enough positive karma
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.34,0:36:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,to enter the kingdom of heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.89,0:36:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, by your commitment to your teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.25,0:36:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,your teacher then becomes your advocate
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.41,0:36:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,before God at the right hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.15,0:36:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He speaks for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.63,0:36:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And she is dedicated to the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.21,0:36:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And I will speak for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.57,0:37:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore, you're admitted
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.63,0:37:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,because it's so,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.40,0:37:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,it's the same in the Lotus Land Buddhism
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.02,0:37:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,where an aspect of the Buddha
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.82,0:37:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,is actually the Buddha.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.74,0:37:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your savior.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.69,0:37:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That you can get to this realm
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.21,0:37:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and the savior then speaks for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.37,0:37:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That you, in and of yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.21,0:37:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,unaided, don't have enough karmic momentum
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.39,0:37:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,to enter that celestial domain, celestial.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.88,0:37:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're asking to enter the celestial.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.72,0:37:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The celestial can be entered
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.86,0:37:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,if you are under the tutelage of a master.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.29,0:37:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The savior then acts differently
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.69,0:37:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,than enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.85,0:37:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Enlightenment on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.37,0:37:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.28,0:37:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I will speak for you before the father
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.52,0:37:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,at the right hand of the father
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.88,0:37:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,because of your dedication to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.65,0:37:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.71,0:37:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.01,0:38:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,when you speak of forces that are hostile to us,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.56,0:38:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,to an enlightened seeker
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.82,0:38:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,or a seeker of enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.54,0:38:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.98,0:38:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It kicks back in me
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.54,0:38:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,to old Christian teachings
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.70,0:38:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that I judged were fear-based
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.00,0:38:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,being hostile beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.01,0:38:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Demons, possession, that type of stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.79,0:38:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what you're talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.50,0:38:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And if so, are there practical defenses
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.28,0:38:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,that we who are not enlightened yet
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.28,0:38:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,can take or should take?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.20,0:38:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You just follow your spiritual path.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.51,0:38:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, like I say, power over the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.18,0:38:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,power over the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.73,0:38:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,is lost as integrity takes,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.13,0:38:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,as integrity gets more and stronger
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.07,0:38:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and stronger,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.31,0:38:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,than as you saw on Wall Street,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.69,0:38:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,real calm when all of them began to fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.31,0:39:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, they would consider integrity
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.49,0:39:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,to be their enemy
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.41,0:39:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,because it would be their unmasking.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.65,0:39:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be whipping the sheep's clothing
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.87,0:39:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,off the wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.15,0:39:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.31,0:39:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is more internal
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.72,0:39:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,as far as...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.96,0:39:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.22,0:39:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.97,0:39:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's enough to make you paranoid.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.91,0:39:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.92,0:39:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.48,0:39:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.02,0:39:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What you're talking about
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.88,0:39:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,is the paranoia, the paranoid fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.30,0:39:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That as you reach a higher and higher level,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.96,0:39:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.66,0:39:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It attracts that which is your antithesis
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.28,0:39:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,to try and attack it
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.25,0:39:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,because it feels threatened by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.09,0:39:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, falsehood feels threatened by truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.55,0:39:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That is so.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.14,0:39:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And the more it feels threatened,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.44,0:39:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,the more vociferous it gets,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.40,0:39:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,the louder it yells,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.72,0:39:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and the more savagely it attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.50,0:39:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that not so?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.56,0:39:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.82,0:39:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,How popular is...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.54,0:40:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,How popular is it to quote from the Constitution
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.42,0:40:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,that Congress shall make no law
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.82,0:40:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,prohibiting...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.02,0:40:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No, establishing religion
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.60,0:40:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,nor prohibiting the free exercise thereof?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.90,0:40:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,How popular is the last half of that sentence?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.33,0:40:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't heard a one.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.67,0:40:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the conservative religious people
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.31,0:40:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,quote the Constitution correctly.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.56,0:40:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Nor prohibit the free exercise thereof.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.34,0:40:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, can't they read English?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.06,0:40:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.30,0:40:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.12,0:40:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,if I choose to emphasize that,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.40,0:40:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,get to be a blogger,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.44,0:40:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,blog it all over the place,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.96,0:40:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,write letters to everybody,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.78,0:40:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll arouse that which is hostile to that viewpoint.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.98,0:40:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.44,0:41:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Nor prohibit the free exercise thereof.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.62,0:41:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Santa Claus.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.70,0:41:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.02,0:41:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.52,0:41:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The study group that I belong to
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.59,0:41:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,has been...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.87,0:41:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,focusing on prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.65,0:41:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's an old saying
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.79,0:41:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,that we should pray
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.85,0:41:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,as though everything depends upon God
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.33,0:41:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and work as though everything depends upon us.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.73,0:41:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And how does that calibrate?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.03,0:41:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a neat saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.52,0:41:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the first part of the sentence again?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.58,0:41:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You pray as though everything depends upon God.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.54,0:41:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.22,0:41:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You're totally dependent on God, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.76,0:42:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, work as though everything depended on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.59,0:42:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.07,0:42:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Put forth your most effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.55,0:42:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to know what that quote calibrates that?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.43,0:42:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.93,0:42:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.77,0:42:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to quote that.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.42,0:42:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over 350,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.10,0:42:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,380,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.40,0:42:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,390,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.66,0:42:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,400,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.44,0:42:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,395,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.00,0:42:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,400,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.80,0:42:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,395.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.86,0:42:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.86,0:42:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it change if,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.96,0:42:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of saying work as though everything depends upon us,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.54,0:42:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,to say be,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.25,0:42:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,to be,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.45,0:42:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,does that alter the...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.45,0:42:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it change?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.31,0:42:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The call it calibration to be because to work is to do and to do calibrates lower than to be from...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.08,0:42:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't really matter what it calibrates.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.88,0:42:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.48,0:42:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's integrous.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.88,0:42:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.38,0:42:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's taking responsibility at the same time acknowledging the sovereignty of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.08,0:43:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's a very excellent saying, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.68,0:43:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.93,0:43:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's similar to the 12-step group say, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.75,0:43:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,you're responsible for the effort, but not the result.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.34,0:43:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're accountable for the effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.64,0:43:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The result is up to an altitude of forces, karmic and otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.24,0:43:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.24,0:43:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That you can't have anything to do with it, but you're karmically rewarded by having done the best you can,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.72,0:43:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,so far as you see your responsibility, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.84,0:43:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.25,0:43:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.25,0:43:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.25,0:43:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.25,0:43:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.03,0:43:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.17,0:43:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, in truth versus falsehood,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.28,0:43:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,you included a chart calibrating ancient societies.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.58,0:44:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The ones that calibrated by far the highest was Atlantis.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.50,0:44:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,When and where was Atlantis?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.60,0:44:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I didn't calibrate the level of Atlantis.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.50,0:44:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I calibrated Atlantis was an actual reality rather than a fantasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.23,0:44:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It says it was a reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.53,0:44:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.13,0:44:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You said it was a 295.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.63,0:44:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.03,0:44:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.86,0:44:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.56,0:44:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Historical societies.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.82,0:44:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It calibrated 290, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.72,0:44:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.22,0:44:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.72,0:44:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Just...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.22,0:44:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it did exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.72,0:44:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what we...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.42,0:44:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.72,0:44:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, we got a confirmation of its location, even.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.72,0:44:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.92,0:44:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And that was where?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.32,0:44:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I forget now.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.86,0:44:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.16,0:44:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I think they closed up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.46,0:44:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.96,0:44:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a very ancient society?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.66,0:44:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, before our recorded history, or is it...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.46,0:44:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Before our recorded history, well, don't forget Plato.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.66,0:44:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.06,0:44:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.46,0:44:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, recounted the history of Atlantis.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.56,0:44:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.36,0:44:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.56,0:44:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There is much...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.46,0:44:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.76,0:44:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And we did calibrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.16,0:45:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There was research that indicated its location.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.75,0:45:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And I forget where that location was.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.85,0:45:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There were several provisional locations.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.85,0:45:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They were not correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.75,0:45:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But there was one they did get the other correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.65,0:45:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.35,0:45:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The Greek isle someplace.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.95,0:45:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We weren't supposed to share it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.15,0:45:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.45,0:45:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.15,0:45:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.75,0:45:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry about the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.35,0:45:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.45,0:45:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.45,0:45:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we got...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.45,0:45:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We couldn't share it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.00,0:45:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.60,0:45:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.00,0:45:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.90,0:45:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.80,0:45:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.54,0:45:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You're thinking of the...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.54,0:45:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're thinking of Cayce.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.30,0:45:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Cayce's readings on Atlantis.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.60,0:45:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.10,0:45:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.76,0:45:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.26,0:45:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But I mean, we got...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.06,0:45:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.46,0:45:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.96,0:45:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.46,0:45:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.26,0:45:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.76,0:45:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is in regards to the evolution of human consciousness and in regards to
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.46,0:45:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,group.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.96,0:45:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You say that we come all in together and sometimes we leave together.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.06,0:45:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.36,0:45:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It sort of is.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.16,0:45:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.96,0:45:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So, with realms ranging from the lower astrals all the way up to the celestial realms, what's
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.06,0:45:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,the difference?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.46,0:45:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.56,0:45:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.76,0:45:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.86,0:45:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.96,0:46:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.06,0:46:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.16,0:46:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.26,0:46:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.36,0:46:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.46,0:46:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.56,0:46:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.66,0:46:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.86,0:46:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.96,0:46:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.06,0:46:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.16,0:46:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.26,0:46:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.46,0:46:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.76,0:46:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.26,0:46:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What happens when we are not on the earth plane?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.86,0:46:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.56,0:46:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a human...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.12,0:46:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The classic answer is the inner planes, that you stay out, you're out, you're in spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.10,0:46:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and not a physicality and that you reincarnate when no group decides it's for the benefit
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.52,0:46:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,of everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.16,0:46:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if they vote or what, everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.66,0:46:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We tend to come in together.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.36,0:46:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.86,0:46:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I think by attraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.16,0:46:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.66,0:46:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We tend to group together by attraction, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.79,0:46:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our flock, and our flock is starting to leave, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.47,0:46:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So if we're a bunch of pelicans and a bunch of them start to leave,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.35,0:46:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,hey, we join the flock because everybody's going back, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.67,0:46:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What about, you said that the human life is like a videotape
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.31,0:46:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,with an ending already apparently within it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.57,0:46:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What about humanness as a reality?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.75,0:47:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What about what?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.65,0:47:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Humanness.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.33,0:47:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Like the physicality of humanness as a society.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.07,0:47:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there an end in the tape, our story?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.75,0:47:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And if so, would there be another realm with physicalness?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.23,0:47:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.03,0:47:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Evolutionary-wise, you mean as a group or as an individual?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.41,0:47:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,As a group, as human.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.85,0:47:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,As mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.81,0:47:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,As mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.45,0:47:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Does mankind eventually, collectively, my picture of it,
