Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.35,0:47:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,my picture of it is that will they all eventually transcend physicality?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.43,0:47:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it means that we're not done with what we've got to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.28,0:47:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,but we're doing it in a different realm, in a higher dimension, you know.
