Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.64,0:47:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Earth the only physical, karmic reality?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.52,0:47:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I never asked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.88,0:47:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I have permission to ask about Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.32,0:47:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Earth is the only human, physical, planetary habitat at this time, or is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.16,0:48:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.80,0:48:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
