Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.46,1:14:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Assist.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.22,1:14:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, and that was our goal.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.58,1:14:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we were going to use technology as well as any other means.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.90,1:14:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And if the technology doesn't work,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.90,1:14:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,is there anything else that you could recommend that we...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.72,1:14:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, surrender the world to God, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.72,1:15:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Let God worry about the evolution of human consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.91,1:15:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And so do we...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:05.91,1:15:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Do anything...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.00,1:15:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Education.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.29,1:15:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Education, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:12.29,1:15:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So recommend...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.29,1:15:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,For all of mankind, education, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:15.29,1:15:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I think of all the things that people can do for others,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.71,1:15:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,education is the only one that works.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.71,1:15:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So provide education so that they could...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:23.89,1:15:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Education is the only thing that works.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.89,1:15:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.05,1:15:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point in giving poor people money
Dialogue: 0,1:15:29.05,1:15:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,because they will probably get poor all over again.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.05,1:15:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:32.05,1:15:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Because if they know how to handle money, they wouldn't be poor.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.05,1:15:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're giving it to their own person.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:37.78,1:15:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What you want to do is provide the circumstances for them to thrive.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.85,1:15:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And research education is the greatest, the greatest benefit.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.07,1:15:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Every dollar spent on education more than pays for itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.30,1:15:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So there is no technology available from your experience, exposure,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:54.30,1:15:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,that has done any helping of anything...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.30,1:16:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know of any technology.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:00.30,1:16:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:01.30,1:16:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.33,1:16:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.89,1:16:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The steam engine, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.25,1:16:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The water wheel.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.25,1:16:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The wheel.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.25,1:16:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, by God, the wheel.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.25,1:16:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right, Steve.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.47,1:16:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The wheel.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.47,1:16:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I want to thank you for all that you do
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.47,1:16:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and thank you for answering so many questions.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.47,1:16:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a, you know, kind of a feeling or a knowingness that I came upon
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.47,1:16:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,a week or so ago, and I just wanted to discuss it
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.50,1:16:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,or see what you had to say with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.50,1:16:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And the idea is that I felt that if I'm able to transcend
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.50,1:16:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,this material experience form, if I transcend this form,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.63,1:16:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,am I transcending all form at the same time?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.43,1:16:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If you transcend form as form, transcend the non-linear,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.43,1:16:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,you're at 850.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.43,1:16:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.43,1:17:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you don't have to worry about it
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.42,1:17:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,because it has no reality.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.42,1:17:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't like you have to decline it.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.19,1:17:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not an option.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.47,1:17:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.81,1:17:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.57,1:17:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I am a psychology student in Flagstaff,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:32.57,1:17:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and I was a little surprised that Freud calibrates at 499.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.57,1:17:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.57,1:17:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Freud, yes, 499, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.57,1:17:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And then today when you had the slides up,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.57,1:17:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,so Freud calibrates higher than what?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.57,1:17:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,William James or Shakespeare.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.57,1:17:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And I know you said it means not better than.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.57,1:17:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see, what is your question again?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.57,1:17:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the question...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.57,1:17:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants to know why that Freud is at 499.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.57,1:18:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Freud calibrated at 499, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.57,1:18:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the next thing?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.57,1:18:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he calibrated higher than Shakespeare.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.57,1:18:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Same thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.57,1:18:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I can't compare it with...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:07.57,1:18:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't compare apples and oranges.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.57,1:18:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, my question is, does that mean I have to hold
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.57,1:18:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Freud's ideas with so much truth?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.57,1:18:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.70,1:18:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Because a lot of his...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:17.70,1:18:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't compare it to...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.70,1:18:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was the other person?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:19.70,1:18:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea who you're comparing.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:20.70,1:18:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.70,1:18:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not comparing him.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.70,1:18:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You said Freud at 499 and what?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.70,1:18:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,She's just...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:24.70,1:18:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean I have to hold his...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.70,1:18:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, who was the other person she compared him to?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.70,1:18:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,William James.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:28.70,1:18:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,William James.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:29.70,1:18:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,William James, he was 490.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.70,1:18:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And that, you know, surprised me, but then...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.70,1:18:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,These are different levels that they're expressing, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.73,1:18:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Freud, like Einstein.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:37.73,1:18:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Einstein is also at 499.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.73,1:18:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Also Sir Isaac Newton.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.73,1:18:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,All geniuses...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.73,1:18:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.73,1:18:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,...took the level of genius to the ultimate.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:46.73,1:18:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you've got to jump paradigms.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.73,1:18:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So does this mean I have to...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.04,1:18:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So at 499, Einstein said,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:54.04,1:18:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I prefer to believe that there's an independent objective universe out there
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.04,1:19:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,that exists independent of human consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.04,1:19:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And he rejected 500.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.04,1:19:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Because at 500, you move from the linear Newtonian paradigm
Dialogue: 0,1:19:08.04,1:19:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,to subjectivity as the ultimate reality.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.04,1:19:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't live within symbols.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.04,1:19:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I live within subjective experiential.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.04,1:19:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:17.04,1:19:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's over 500, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.04,1:19:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.04,1:19:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So does that...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.33,1:19:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I find so many of Freud's ideas nuts and...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.33,1:19:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You find Freud's ideas nuts?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.33,1:19:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So many of Freud's ideas I find nuts.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.33,1:19:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean as a concept?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.33,1:19:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.33,1:19:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Experientially, you ever go through a Freudian psychoanalysis?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.33,1:19:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll see how...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.33,1:19:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll find out different.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.33,1:19:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that's my point then.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.33,1:19:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, do I hold Freud as a genius like Einstein?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.33,1:19:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He is a genius, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:43.33,1:19:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.55,1:19:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, you're too young to realize that.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.55,1:19:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.55,1:19:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too young to realize the impact he had on all generations.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.55,1:19:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Freud's discoveries of the unconscious turned everything around.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.55,1:19:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Had a major impact.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.51,1:20:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Changed the whole paradigm of responsibility, sexuality, intention.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.99,1:20:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like the women's revolution of becoming equal with men.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.99,1:20:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It just changes the whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.28,1:20:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a whole different way of holding value and the...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.28,1:20:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Freud's main genius was in discovering the unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:18.28,1:20:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And the powerful effect that it has in the unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.28,1:20:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And the fact that the unconscious is unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.28,1:20:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Carl Jung was...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.57,1:20:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Carl Jung was 520.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:28.57,1:20:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Carl Jung also explored the unconscious, but he included the spiritual as a reality,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:33.57,1:20:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,whereas Freud did not.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:34.57,1:20:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.57,1:20:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Freud looked at the anthropomorphic God and said, because God is traditionally depicted
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.07,1:20:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,as anthropomorphic, obviously a projection of man's own unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.07,1:20:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Then he made the invalid conclusion, therefore God doesn't exist.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.07,1:20:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he should have said, therefore the irrational, you know, in my own writings,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:54.58,1:21:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I reject the anthropomorphic depictions of God as primitive projection from the, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:00.58,1:21:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,primitive onto divinity.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.58,1:21:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,God makes the volcanoes, God makes the earthquakes, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:05.58,1:21:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:07.35,1:21:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So put Carl Jung on the pedestal.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:09.35,1:21:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Carl Jung.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.35,1:21:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not up there.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.35,1:21:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Freud discovered the unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:14.35,1:21:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That was his main discovery and the power of the unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:17.35,1:21:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And then Jung carried it further and included it.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.35,1:21:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He included the spiritual dimension.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.35,1:21:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Jung that discovered synchronicity.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.35,1:21:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It was because of Carl Jung's honesty that the whole 12-step movement arose.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.35,1:21:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Without Carl Jung, Bill W. never would have gotten this over, nor would have anybody who
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.67,1:21:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,preceded him.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:40.67,1:21:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:42.67,1:21:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a psychology student, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.67,1:21:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's a fun trip.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.67,1:21:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.67,1:21:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure is.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:48.67,1:21:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,God help you, woman.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.67,1:21:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The jungle of psychology, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.67,1:21:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,All the different theories and, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:51.67,1:22:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, before I have heard you speak about how one could own a quality of God,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.38,1:22:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,be that quality kindness or politeness or love or another quality, is owning a quality
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.38,1:22:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,of God the same as contemplating on that quality?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.38,1:22:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:19.95,1:22:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Contemplating it, realizing it that is innate within yourself as well.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.95,1:22:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That that quality that we call divine is intrinsic to yourself also.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.74,1:22:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,A mouse got caught in a mouse trap, you know, a sticky pad.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.74,1:22:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't come to the lecture until I went out and relieved the mouse of the slow torture
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.74,1:22:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,of slowly dying of suffocation and starvation and dehydration from the quick mercy death.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.67,1:22:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stand the thought that he's going to be left there to suffer and suffer and
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.02,1:22:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,suffer.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.02,1:22:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,On the other hand, that's also something you could let go of and say you're just projecting
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.11,1:22:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,that onto the mouse.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.11,1:22:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see how you handled it?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.11,1:22:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it merciful to put him to sleep?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.11,1:22:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it more merciful to let it be?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.24,1:23:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I surrender him to God?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.24,1:23:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's God's problem if this mouse lays there and takes two weeks to die of dehydration,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:01.24,1:23:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,right?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.24,1:23:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see the simplest thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.24,1:23:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's how you hold it, how you see it.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.24,1:23:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:05.24,1:23:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I surrendered it to God and put it out of its misery.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:06.24,1:23:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, God has to do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.24,1:23:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He has to do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.24,1:23:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He has to do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:09.24,1:23:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He has to do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.24,1:23:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He has to do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.37,1:23:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He has to do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.37,1:23:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He has to do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.37,1:23:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He has to do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.37,1:23:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He has to do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.37,1:23:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He has to do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.48,1:23:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He has to do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:19.48,1:23:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He has to do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.48,1:23:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He has to do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.48,1:23:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:23.41,1:23:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I surrendered it to God and put it out of its misery.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.41,1:23:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, God has to act through somebody.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:27.14,1:23:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He said, for God's sake, put him to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.14,1:23:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm like, mercy.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.14,1:23:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.14,1:23:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.14,1:23:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Move along quickly now.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.14,1:23:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.14,1:23:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.64,1:23:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no idea that you would be so funny, so I was glad.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:52.63,1:23:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Paramahansa Yogananda, he called enlightenment superconscious.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.63,1:23:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:58.63,1:23:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He called enlightenment superconscious union with God.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.63,1:24:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.63,1:24:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And sleep, deep, deep dreamless sleep, subconscious union with God.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:03.63,1:24:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.63,1:24:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And encouraged his disciples to meditate as much as possible.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.63,1:24:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.63,1:24:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And sleep as little as possible.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:09.63,1:24:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.63,1:24:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm wondering what you think about that instruction, whether that does, in fact, increase
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.07,1:24:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,the possibility or the nature of the waking state toward the extension.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.63,1:24:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The intention behind it, of course, is to meditate as much as possible.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.70,1:24:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:28.70,1:24:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And some spiritual divisions try to cut down on physical sleep.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.70,1:24:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't notice that there's any benefit one way or the other, frankly.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.74,1:24:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.74,1:24:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you ever visit the center there in California?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:42.77,1:24:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I haven't been there, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.77,1:24:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:45.77,1:24:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:47.02,1:24:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Autobiography of a Yogi, he wrote.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.02,1:24:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.02,1:24:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Very famous book.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.38,1:24:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We're almost at the end.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:55.38,1:24:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:58.96,1:25:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.60,1:25:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Just to go back to kinesiology.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.37,1:25:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.37,1:25:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We were at lunch this afternoon, and we were all in disagreement on calibrating by 150
Dialogue: 0,1:25:14.37,1:25:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,points.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.37,1:25:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.37,1:25:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the next question.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.37,1:25:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not too good at it.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.37,1:25:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.37,1:25:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But the point was none of us were, and I've been playing with this for 20 years, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.40,1:25:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,with applied kinesiology.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:28.40,1:25:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the question is that, apart from just calibrating, you know, if I give, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:34.23,1:25:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,five members in the audience 10 or 20 yes or no questions to which we have yes or no
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.23,1:25:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,answers.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.23,1:25:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.23,1:25:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,They won't agree.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.23,1:25:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,They won't agree.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.23,1:25:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And how many of them will get 19 out of 20 right?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.23,1:25:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Or even 10 out of 20 right?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.23,1:25:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So, then the next question that becomes is what about the reliability of the test?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:48.23,1:25:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Because before we put our arm out here and test for something, you've got to make sure
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.23,1:25:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,the ruler is.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.23,1:25:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I can answer it, because I know your whole lecture.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.23,1:25:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.23,1:25:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And it has to do with internal consistency.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.23,1:25:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That every two people have to be able to do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.23,1:25:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.23,1:25:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the question is, what about the reliability of the test?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.23,1:25:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Because before we put our arm out here and test for something, you've got to make sure
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.23,1:25:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,the ruler is.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:58.23,1:25:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I can answer it, because I know your whole lecture.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.23,1:26:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.23,1:26:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That every two people will maybe vary from another two people, but they will be internally
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.19,1:26:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,consistent.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.19,1:26:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.19,1:26:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, there's a proficiency and a skill.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:15.44,1:26:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Very few people, why were you doing this at lunch?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:17.64,1:26:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I know why you were doing it.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.86,1:26:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why you're getting varying answers already.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.96,1:26:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I already got why you're doing it at lunch.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.96,1:26:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I wasn't doing it.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:26.41,1:26:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I was on looking as two other people were doing it.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:29.75,1:26:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's how it all came up.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.75,1:26:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Not by you.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.75,1:26:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm using the generic term.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.75,1:26:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The group.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:33.75,1:26:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.67,1:26:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.67,1:26:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know the basics of kinesiology all the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.71,1:26:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Your intention has to be to just know the truth of a thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:44.39,1:26:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't have any gain in it.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.37,1:26:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be out to try to prove or disprove that kinesiology works or is accurate.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:51.11,1:26:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, so many people come at it with a challenge.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:55.10,1:26:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The minute you come at it with a challenge, you just blew it.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:59.53,1:27:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a very simple thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:01.19,1:27:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I showed it so simply that it seems to me, you know, you've got to be really, really
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.57,1:27:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,stupid to not get it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:07.81,1:27:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to show it one more time.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.70,1:27:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to show it one last time.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:11.70,1:27:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And if one more person brings up a question about kinesiology, I'm going to throw them
Dialogue: 0,1:27:16.26,1:27:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,into the pits.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.26,1:27:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Good God.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:20.12,1:27:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's so dumb.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.48,1:27:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me your arm.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:37.03,1:27:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the top picture and now resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:41.32,1:27:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the top picture and now resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:45.29,1:27:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the bottom picture.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:47.01,1:27:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Now resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.01,1:27:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, Jesus, you don't have to go to college, do you?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:53.54,1:27:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,To make it any more complicated than that is deliberate confusion.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:57.60,1:28:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That they project onto it because they want to adopt some kind of an argumentative position.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.72,1:28:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.43,1:28:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You just saw the truth of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:05.43,1:28:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,End of the problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.65,1:28:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But did you see, it's not, I mean, you know, it's not as simple or as easy as that.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:07.65,1:28:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.55,1:28:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's what you think.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:10.55,1:28:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It is as simple as that.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:11.55,1:28:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:12.55,1:28:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The point is.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:13.55,1:28:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, he missed the point altogether, I see.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:15.86,1:28:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to turn it into an intellectual understanding?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.86,1:28:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:17.86,1:28:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:19.21,1:28:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.21,1:28:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:21.21,1:28:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.21,1:28:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:23.21,1:28:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.21,1:28:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:25.21,1:28:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.21,1:28:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:27.21,1:28:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.40,1:28:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.40,1:28:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.40,1:28:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:31.40,1:28:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.40,1:28:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What is your problem?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.40,1:28:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:34.40,1:28:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:35.40,1:28:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.40,1:28:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,On a clinical setting.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.40,1:28:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I deal with chronic pain.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:40.40,1:28:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We've done studies on this.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:41.40,1:28:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, so I've been with this for 20 years.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.40,1:28:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm not just asking about it flippantly.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:47.40,1:28:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The question is that how does it become consistent?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.40,1:28:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you not let your own bias fly into the test?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:54.40,1:28:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just what I got through telling you.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.40,1:28:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.40,1:28:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't have a bias.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.40,1:28:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:58.40,1:29:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But it sometimes creeps in without even knowing it's creeping in.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.40,1:29:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:01.40,1:29:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's when the test becomes wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.40,1:29:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's a matter of integrity.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:03.40,1:29:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why people over, under 200 can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.40,1:29:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You know that people under 200 cannot be integrists?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:05.40,1:29:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,They cannot make a statement without having a position about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:06.40,1:29:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not possible because they're wrong brain physiology from the left brain.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.40,1:29:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So when they try to imitate it, they always get a falsehood because they're supposed to.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.40,1:29:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only when you get over 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:09.40,1:29:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So when they try to imitate it, they always get a falsehood because they're supposed to.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.20,1:29:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only when you get over 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:31.23,1:29:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:32.23,1:29:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So when they try to imitate it, they always get a falsehood because they're supposed to.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:34.12,1:29:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only when you get over 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.12,1:29:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you adopt the positionality?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.12,1:29:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you vote for, let's say, a party that you think is the best for the government instead
Dialogue: 0,1:29:41.96,1:29:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,of a party that's best for me?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.85,1:29:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Below 200, I vote for him because he's going to be good to the cab drivers.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:50.47,1:29:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Over 200, I vote for the mayor that I think is going to be the best for the city.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:55.03,1:29:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the difference.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.03,1:29:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.22,1:29:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:58.22,1:29:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:00.99,1:30:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And now we've got to stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.99,1:30:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll throw us out.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:03.37,1:30:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Be quick.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.37,1:30:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Be quick.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:05.37,1:30:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'll be quick.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.24,1:30:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll answer you quick.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:08.24,1:30:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.43,1:30:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I'm afraid of being thrown into the pits now.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.43,1:30:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:11.43,1:30:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you might get it, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:12.43,1:30:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is regarding just research, the kind of research that you do.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.43,1:30:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you typically calibrate things yourself and have teams confirm it?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.43,1:30:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you just stick with what you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:15.43,1:30:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we do it all different kinds of ways.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:16.43,1:30:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been doing it for some 25, 30 years.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.43,1:30:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And I learned it from other people who were already doing it.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:18.43,1:30:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't invent it.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.43,1:30:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's the method that you're using now?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.43,1:30:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we've been doing it for some 25, 30 years.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:21.43,1:30:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And I learned it from other people who were already doing it.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:22.43,1:30:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't invent it.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:23.43,1:30:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's the method that you're using now?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:24.43,1:30:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we do it all different kinds of ways.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:25.43,1:30:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been doing it for some 25, 30 years.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:26.43,1:30:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And I learned it from other people who were already doing it.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.43,1:30:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't invent it.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:28.43,1:30:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's the method that you're using now?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:29.43,1:30:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I just demonstrated it.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:30.43,1:30:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I just got through demonstrating it.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:31.43,1:30:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm just talking about like with other people.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:32.43,1:30:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you, you know, having it confirmed or what's the method you use for confirmation?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:33.43,1:30:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if I want confirmation.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:34.43,1:30:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to know what somebody else gets because they're then running, see, it runs
Dialogue: 0,1:30:35.59,1:30:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,on your own scale.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.59,1:30:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you know, I don't know if I want confirmation.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:37.59,1:30:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to know what somebody else gets because they're then running, see, it runs
Dialogue: 0,1:30:54.60,1:30:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,on your own scale.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:55.60,1:30:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can adopt any scale you want.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.40,1:31:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You can say 10 is true and 1 is not true and 5 is halfway between.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.66,1:31:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You can set up your own scale.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:06.66,1:31:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:07.66,1:31:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you will be integrous within your own scale, but not in my scale.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:15.45,1:31:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If I set the barometric pressure as normal, so-and-so.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.45,1:31:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So if I have a different thermometer, if I say on my thermometer 0 is freezing and 212
Dialogue: 0,1:31:24.45,1:31:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,is boiling, then that, on that thermometer, I will get that.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:27.45,1:31:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You can make your own thermometer and you'll get different figures.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:30.45,1:31:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:31.77,1:31:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So you couldn't have people use your scale?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:33.77,1:31:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.77,1:31:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Other people use our scale.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:35.77,1:31:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And I say, you know, based on this scale of 1 to 1,000, you know, this calibrates it,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:42.32,1:31:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,so-and-so.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:43.32,1:31:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see how you could get disparities if you're doing it integrously.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:47.32,1:31:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to a lecture recently and they were saying that you use teams to...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.32,1:31:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:52.38,1:31:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, because if you do it this way, yeah, you can also do it, you know, the O-ring.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:57.38,1:31:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need a team.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:58.38,1:31:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.38,1:32:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:00.38,1:32:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So if I hold Abraham Lincoln in mind, I'm going to hold Abraham Lincoln in mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:05.38,1:32:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.33,1:32:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I'm holding somebody else in mind who says, we worship death.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.46,1:32:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no comparison.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:18.52,1:32:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The moment I hold this image in mind, I can't, I've got no strength.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:22.58,1:32:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But when I hold Abraham Lincoln in mind, it's simple.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:26.09,1:32:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:27.19,1:32:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.19,1:32:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry about teams.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:29.19,1:32:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Teams.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:31.18,1:32:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You just have people who work together and they get intuitively aligned with each other
Dialogue: 0,1:32:35.18,1:32:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and they can work very fast, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:38.27,1:32:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:39.27,1:32:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:40.27,1:32:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:41.27,1:32:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes spouses can't work together for unknown reasons and the two of them have
Dialogue: 0,1:32:46.13,1:32:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,to find a second, another person.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:48.13,1:32:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you get disparity, try working with yourself for a while until you get consistency.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:54.26,1:32:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a simpler method which I also explained last time and that's the end of the questions.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:59.52,1:33:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to be a genius to do this.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.52,1:33:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You lift the dictionary.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:02.52,1:33:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You hold Abraham Lincoln in mind, you know, big heavy dictionary.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:06.52,1:33:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And you see how much strength it takes to lift the dictionary with Abraham Lincoln.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.52,1:33:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you hold Bin Laden in mind and see how much strength it takes.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.52,1:33:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll see a marked difference.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:17.52,1:33:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you don't have to go to college.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:19.52,1:33:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to be a, you know, advanced physicist to do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:26.12,1:33:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Simple.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.24,1:33:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's so simple, that's why it's hard to see.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:30.24,1:33:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And in doing that, I would get my own level of truth with regards to that.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:34.08,1:33:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously, I might not get your level of truth because we're in different places.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:38.08,1:33:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I'm a little bit more interested in yours than I am in mine.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:43.08,1:33:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You can say on a level of one to a thousand.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:46.08,1:33:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, according to this scale, this statement calibrates to start with as true or not true.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:54.08,1:33:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you can try to get a number.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:56.08,1:33:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget we've done it thousands of times.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:58.08,1:34:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget that I'm extremely intuitive.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:00.08,1:34:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see the essence of a thing before it speaks.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:03.08,1:34:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I mean, I've already got the number in my mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:05.08,1:34:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't tell her what the number is.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:07.08,1:34:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, we'll bring up something like this in my mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:10.17,1:34:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,As I raise my hand, I've got, it's about 480 in my, you know, just a knowingness.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.17,1:34:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't tell her what I'm holding in mind, but it says the number.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:18.17,1:34:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And then she gets to 480.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:19.17,1:34:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It just confirms.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:21.17,1:34:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't mean I'm accurate all the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:23.17,1:34:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I trained myself to know the temperature.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:25.17,1:34:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I got an 84 caddy.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:26.17,1:34:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And the thing I liked about it best, other than the fact that it's low down and gorgeous,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:31.17,1:34:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:32.17,1:34:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Just got repainted, oh boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:35.17,1:34:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's got a thermometer.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:36.17,1:34:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You push the button, it tells you the outside temperature.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:39.17,1:34:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So I trained myself, because I had to get up every morning in the dark and the cold and drive.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:43.17,1:34:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And I trained myself to say what the temperature is before I hit the button.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:47.17,1:34:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I found within a matter of months, I was so accurate,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:50.49,1:34:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I could predict the temperature outside within a degree or two almost 99% of the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:55.49,1:35:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd go out to the car, and I would just know it's 64.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:00.71,1:35:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd hit the button, it'd be 64.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:02.71,1:35:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So I did that over and over again to train myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:05.71,1:35:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And I did it as an experiment.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:07.71,1:35:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And then once you were trained, you knew you were trained, and you didn't need to be prepared.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:10.71,1:35:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So, yes, I trained myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:12.71,1:35:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore, I could tell the temperature within a matter of degrees.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:16.71,1:35:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's just experiential.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:19.12,1:35:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,See what I'm saying there?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:20.12,1:35:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's experiential.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:22.12,1:35:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Trial and error.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.12,1:35:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And we've got to get out of here at 530, they say.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:25.12,1:35:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:27.12,1:35:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If you make it very fast, I mean by very fast, get to the essence of it quick.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.12,1:35:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Want a picture?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:32.12,1:35:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it quick.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:33.12,1:35:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:34.12,1:35:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lag.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.12,1:35:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't drag.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:36.12,1:35:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Jump along.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:38.22,1:35:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Step lively.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:39.22,1:35:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Step lively.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:40.22,1:35:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Slip lively.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:41.22,1:35:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Slip lively.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:42.22,1:35:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Blast.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:47.84,1:35:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Slip lively, or it's the gangplank for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:52.58,1:35:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:53.58,1:35:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the last, though.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:55.58,1:35:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, quick question.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:57.58,1:36:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Since we're talking about spiritual teachers, and you didn't have that other list that you mentioned.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:01.58,1:36:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:02.58,1:36:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering if,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:03.58,1:36:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,because I've been following this path for a long time, for about 10 years.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:06.58,1:36:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:07.58,1:36:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,For the cryon energy, and the cryon channelings.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:10.58,1:36:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to know what they ...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:13.03,1:36:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a big, that's an entity on the other side?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:18.34,1:36:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:19.34,1:36:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I don't do channelers from the other side.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:21.34,1:36:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's interdimensional, and I've been following that path, and it says a lot of the same things you've been saying.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:28.00,1:36:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, good.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:29.00,1:36:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:30.00,1:36:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No more of you asking me.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:32.00,1:36:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So I want to know if it's higher or lower, or what.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:37.00,1:36:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's legitimate to ask that.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:40.00,1:36:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The essence of the spiritual truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:44.82,1:36:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's, for me, should I follow it anymore?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:48.82,1:36:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sincere in what I do.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:50.82,1:36:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We can ask that one.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:51.82,1:36:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You can ask that one.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:52.82,1:36:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be ...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:53.82,1:36:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to ask the question.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:56.82,1:37:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for her to continue with this teacher, resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:02.77,1:37:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You asked.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:03.77,1:37:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:12.08,1:37:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:13.08,1:37:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Come up.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:14.08,1:37:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you what happens.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:16.08,1:37:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there ...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:17.08,1:37:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing wrong with following things that don't calibrate real high, because they serve a purpose up to a certain point.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:24.52,1:37:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to make a lot of mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:26.52,1:37:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes, you know ...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:28.52,1:37:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And it serves a purpose, because after all, first of all, you're intended for ...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:33.52,1:37:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It was her spiritual integrity that drove her to the teacher.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:37.52,1:37:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't the teacher that has the spiritual integrity.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:39.52,1:37:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the student.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:41.97,1:37:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,They follow all kinds of crooks out of their own inner honesty.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:46.32,1:37:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, baby.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:47.32,1:37:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This is God's love.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.32,1:37:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's be godly.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:50.32,1:37:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it happens every day.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:52.32,1:37:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Women write books on, you know, gurus I've been seduced by.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:56.32,1:37:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a book.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:58.32,1:37:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got them at home.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:59.32,1:38:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, the story about all the gurus and the rap that he gave her.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:02.32,1:38:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It was her sincerity, her integrity, her honesty, her innocence that was ravished, you see?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:08.39,1:38:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So I think a teacher, you know, doesn't have to calibrate a 900 to be useful.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:14.39,1:38:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You can follow a false teacher for a while.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:16.39,1:38:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And now you've learned a lot.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:18.39,1:38:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You've learned a lot.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:19.39,1:38:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you've learned how to be a devotee.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:21.39,1:38:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You've learned self-sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:23.39,1:38:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You've learned humility.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:25.39,1:38:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And now you move to a higher teacher.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:27.39,1:38:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But, so ...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:32.86,1:38:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, higher teachers and myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:33.86,1:38:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a question here with an email answer in case I didn't get up here.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:37.86,1:38:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:38.86,1:38:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is, why is Mary Baker Eddy not a part of the significant spiritual leadership
Dialogue: 0,1:38:46.86,1:38:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,you calibrate?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:48.86,1:38:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I picked more ancient ones.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:51.86,1:38:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Mary Baker Eddy, of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:53.86,1:38:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Four of her students.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:55.86,1:38:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Joel Goldsmith.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:56.86,1:38:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:57.86,1:38:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Phil Morris.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:58.86,1:38:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I forget.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:59.86,1:39:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know why.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:00.86,1:39:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably just prejudice against women, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:01.86,1:39:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:09.28,1:39:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I know her name wasn't ...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:10.28,1:39:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought there must be a really good reason.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:11.28,1:39:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No, because, you know, you have to know how we put this together.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:16.28,1:39:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's 144, but we had hundreds, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:20.28,1:39:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I think we just took every sixth name or something like that off of her.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:24.28,1:39:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I forget.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:25.28,1:39:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Mary Baker Eddy.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:26.28,1:39:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know, she founded the church.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:27.28,1:39:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,She founded ...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:28.28,1:39:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:29.28,1:39:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And ...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:30.28,1:39:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What, are you fishing for, or what?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:31.28,1:39:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:32.28,1:39:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The Christian Science Monitor is a world-renowned ...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:33.28,1:39:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:34.28,1:39:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,My grandmother was a Christian scientist.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:35.28,1:39:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Christian Science Monitor magazine, you know, calibrates quite high.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:40.28,1:39:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:41.28,1:39:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's just an outstanding group of people and movement.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:44.28,1:39:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:45.28,1:39:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why, you know, I think ...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:46.28,1:39:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,She began the whole New Thought movement, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:47.28,1:39:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,She should be, she ought to be calibrated.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:48.28,1:39:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be very interested.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:49.28,1:39:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Mary Baker Eddy?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:50.28,1:39:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:51.28,1:39:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to do Mary Baker Eddy.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:52.28,1:39:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,She's got her upside, she's got her downside.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:53.28,1:39:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to do Mary, we don't have permission to do her.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:58.79,1:40:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No, come on, I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:01.83,1:40:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Mary Baker Eddy.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:03.73,1:40:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to do Mary Baker Eddy.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:06.87,1:40:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Mary Baker Eddy is over 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:12.89,1:40:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all you really need to know.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:14.23,1:40:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,She's over 300.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.23,1:40:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:16.23,1:40:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,She's over 300, 400, 500, 550, 560.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:21.45,1:40:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm getting false answers.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:23.41,1:40:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting false answers?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:24.69,1:40:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.19,1:40:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of the crowd and the answer.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:26.49,1:40:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't answer accurately right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:28.67,1:40:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all laughing and stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:30.03,1:40:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:30.81,1:40:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, well, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:32.05,1:40:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a good person.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:35.92,1:40:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,My grandmother was a Christian scientist, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:40.88,1:40:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,She used to read me Shakespeare, Christian science,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:44.24,1:40:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and take me to the Baptist church.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:46.36,1:40:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,In the meantime, my grandfather was a Mason,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:51.44,1:40:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,so I got it heavy from all sides, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:55.72,1:40:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you good.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:58.92,1:41:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's the dedication to the truth that you get out of it,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:03.00,1:41:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the pristine nature of truth itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:05.64,1:41:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, how it's expressed varies from teacher to teacher,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:08.12,1:41:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,from era to era, from culture to culture.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:10.70,1:41:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But once you begin to value truth for its own sake,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:17.19,1:41:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,because truth is one of the qualities of divinity,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:20.19,1:41:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,you can follow then the love of truth and become devoted to truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:24.61,1:41:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So devotional non-duality is devoted to,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:27.17,1:41:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,is the devotion to reaching the ultimate truth
Dialogue: 0,1:41:29.93,1:41:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,that is knowable within this dimension.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:33.34,1:41:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And I want to thank you for the loveliness of this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:36.52,1:41:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We want to congratulate the new couple.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:56.77,1:41:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So we say, Gloria in excelsis Deo.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:59.07,1:42:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You are God's gift to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:03.03,1:43:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:06.52,1:43:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The child in us never dies, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:11.64,1:43:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Every day is kindergarten to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:17.72,1:43:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Every day you discover something new and joyful about the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:23.53,1:43:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
